^ Walsh, Shannon. "Bug Hall: 5 Fast Facts You Need to Know". Heavy.com. Retrieved 7 September 2016. 
^ "Harley and The Davidsons". Discovery Channel. Retrieved 7 September 2016. 
^ Ryan, Patrick. "'Harley and the Davidsons' races back in history". USA Today. Retrieved 7 September 2016. 


