Harley-Davidson®



We are a dealer-exclusive designer, manufacturer and distributor of Harley-Davidson® licensed headwear, giftware and collectibles.As a licensee, we work to uphold the strong brand of Harley-Davidson® by creating products that can meet the high quality standard. Annually, we produce 3 collections to be introduced at more than 1,000 dealerships worldwide. Additionally, we produce merchandise for some of Harley-Davidson's special programs; including Police Sheriff Firefighter, Harley-Davidson Riding Academy, Anniversary collections, and many more.







